title: Welcome To My Website
text:
Welcome to my personal website, created using Quarto. My name is Nick Kent. I am a sophomore at Macalester College, and pursuing a major in data science and minors in computer science and economics. Please take a look through this website if you would like to learn more about myself and some of my projects.
To learn more about Quarto websites visit https://quarto.org/docs/websites.
